<h3>Re: how to create wifi hotspot in parrot 3.6</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>A known way is&#160; open settings, scroll down to bottom, click on &quot;Configure,&quot; scroll down to bottom, click on &quot;show advanced options,&quot; scroll down again and change from 5 Ghz to 2.4 Ghz. Save. I hope will help.</p>
</div>
